root: ^That cannot be all of your subordinates?
^Oh stars. What caused this mission to take such a disastrous turn?
^I do not know, but I do know that your kind started it - and influenced my kind in turn.
^Are your kind easily influenced or are your kind superior?
^Fine. Then perhaps our subordinates have not been subordinated properly?
^We will find the cause later. Look! There’s the last of them gathered…
